    "This increases the speed in processing large amounts of data.",
    "Transformer models are trained on unlabelled data, for example Google's BERT trained on the English language Wikipedia and the Brown Corpus.",
    "45 They can then be tweaked for other tasks.",
    "One of the drawbacks is that they do not exist for all languages.",
    "Additionally, the pre-trained versions might still require some finetuning."
